{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：21:52 2026-04-29 HKT<br/>發佈時間：21:52 2026-04-29 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：21:52 2026-04-29 HKT</p><img alt=\"「電玩精英」騎練齊起孖\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ul/sthl_square/4eed6a35422272ce394df6ea58fcebcc/2026-04/r5_8.jpg\"/><p>今晚韋達馬房在第四場憑「紅愛舍」贏馬後，接着在第五場憑「電玩精英」勝出起孖，後駒更贏得韓國馬事會錦標，騎師班德禮亦起孖而回。</p><p>今晚谷草賽事，韋達手風甚順，先在第四場四班千二米以布文策騎的「紅愛舍」贏馬，接着第五場四班千二米韓國馬事會錦標，再以「電玩精英」勝出兼捧盃。</p><p>「電玩精英」轉入韋達馬房後五戰均有獎金收，今晚更取得轉廄後的首捷，省靚招牌，韋達說：「『電玩精英』較早前不時排外檔，影響發揮，馬兒前仗排內檔取勝，今場排一檔有利，加上下完雨，場地有變化，而此馬喜歡跑鬆軟場地，順利贏馬。</p><h2>按下圖睇更多相片：</h2><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/41ea75d7e846179d842b15790d07e1e7/2026-04/5eeb0fdb-34e8-43ff-8f58-ec698e289e0b.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/1448a4a3ee87534f3c56e3a7806abc67/2026-04/6a3698d5-bdf0-49a7-a8f4-48a753fd97b1.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/4767f326e453fc9ff4fa7bbcd18df569/2026-04/7d1d6c5c-c89e-47ef-8442-0fb26d947ce8.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/25307620aea40739ac6878d8a2b84172/2026-04/8f401f85-0830-49bc-852a-c9a8f8bf23e2.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/7cd14e54829f6dcf5a073ed309b35d5c/2026-04/65e5cb0c-93fd-43df-8197-df9028296068.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/f62efad40ca0550af4eadc2b7aae9dfb/2026-04/82efd76a-a0c2-44ee-8814-5eba98a369ae.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/2013d46311c48ba320d3c964659b596d/2026-04/337aee4c-82d0-453c-8980-28a6cf3304c7.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/49e80bae69d04ccef192b74ff622aafb/2026-04/451db8ad-7455-449c-9865-c2d5b4db3b7f.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/1a08107649d1e9d40c33b92d49d5b776/2026-04/0510c0a7-6c2a-4ba1-a880-f1ae68ec4571.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/9e42482520b3d8291e2c92fa4275deee/2026-04/4367801b-87f9-439a-b74a-2d247077ea23.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/be5ce530